Class CodeTester

  • java.lang.Object
    • CodeTester

  • public abstract class CodeTester
extends java.lang.Object
    CodeTester.java Very easy tool to create your own Java code tester. Simply extend this class, make your test methods that start with an underscore and are public void with no parameters: public void _myTestMethod() {}, and then call this class's runTests() function! For some simper and easier to follow information, simply read this project's README.md :)
    Since:
    10/28/16
